&lt;p id="gI4UHR"&gt;Today, the developer is &lt;a href="https://pokemongolive.com/en/post/poi-submission-beta/"&gt;launching a beta&lt;/a&gt; for the program, and it’s pretty limited to start. It’ll only be available to users in South Korea and Brazil, and it’ll be restricted to players who have reached level 40 in the game. Niantic says that the beta “may expand to more trainers or locations over time.”&lt;/p&gt;
